# Builds run a filtered pnpm install inside the image; never copy host/VPS
# node_modules or build artifacts into the build context.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/.vite
.git
.github
e2e
**/*.log
# Never let the local env file leak into build layers (images are env-free;
# all config arrives at runtime).
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
